These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, musical, thriller
4 different pets are kept: fish, turtle, snake, bird
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
5. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the snake##2
6. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | crime     | musical | disaster |
| Pet     | fish     | snake | bird  | turtle      |

