.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, rock, techno
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, spinach, peach, peas
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
2. the person eating peas is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the person eating peas##1
4. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
5. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
6. the person eating raspberry is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop    | techno     | rock  |
| Food     | raspberry    | peach | spinach | peas |

