.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, jazz, pop, rock
City: boston, nizza, london, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
2. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
5. the person traveling to london is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | pop   | house  | rock |
| City           | nizza | san-francisco | london | boston  |

