.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, tennis, basketball, climbing
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, egyptian, indian
1. the indian is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the egyptian##2
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the indian##3
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the argentine is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Sport         | tennis | skateboarding | climbing | basketball  |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | argentine   | indian  | egyptian |

