.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, go, canasta
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, nigerian, russian
1. the argentine is on the right of the chinese##1
2. the person playing go is between the russian and the chinese##2
3. the person playing mah-jongg is the chinese##1
4. the nigerian is on the left of the chinese##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the argentine##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
