3. the person driving the tram is the fan of country##1
4. the fan of country is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
6. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre       | classical | country | techno    | hip-hop      |
| Transport   | taxi       | tram       | snowmobile | skateboard |

