.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, hiking, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, skiing, rowing, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Hobby   | baking     | chess  | woodworking | hiking |
| Sport     | rugby | biathlon | skiing     | rowing    |

