.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, lemon, pumpkin, cauliflower
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, frog, hamster
1. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1
2. the person eating carrot is the person eating carrot##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
5. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
6. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
7. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Food   | carrot | pumpkin  | cauliflower | lemon |
| Pet           | frog     | hamster | bird    | fish     |

