.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, january, august, may
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, manager, musician
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the librarian##3
2. the librarian is on the right of the manager##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the bartender##1
4. the librarian is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Birthday   | january  | december | may  | august      |
| Job    | musician | bartender | manager | librarian |

