.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk, soy-milk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, bellflower, iris, daisy
1. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
4. the person who growslily is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
6. the person who growslily is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta     | cola     | milk          | soy-milk |
| Flower      | lily | bellflower | daisy | iris  |

 